            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q4_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$S_n=3^{n+1}-1$ ومنه $S_n+u_n=5\\times3^n$. ومن $S_n+u_n=405$ نجد $3^n=81=3^4$، إذن $n=4$."
