            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q1_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1.5 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e2_q2",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e2",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "السؤال 2",
          "maxPoints": 1.5,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "بين أنه من أجل كل عدد طبيعي $n$: $u_n=6n+2$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q2_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$u_n=u_0+nr=6n+2$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1.5 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e2_q3",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e2",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "السؤال 3",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أثبت أن العدد $2024$ حد من حدود المتتالية $(u_n)$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q3_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$u_n=2024$ تكافئ $n=337$، ومنه $2024$ حد من حدود المتتالية."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q3_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e2_q4",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e2",
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "label": "السؤال 4",
          "maxPoints": 2,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q4_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "نضع من أجل كل عدد طبيعي $n$: $S_n=u_0+u_1+\\cdots+u_n$. أ) احسب بدلالة $n$ المجموع $S_n$. ب) عين قيمة العدد الطبيعي $n$ حتى يكون $S_n=352$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q4_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$S_n=\\frac{n+1}{2}(u_0+u_n)=(n+1)(3n+2)$. ومن $S_n=352$ نجد $3n^2+5n-350=0$، ومنه $n=10$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q4_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "2 نقطتان."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3",
          "nodeType": "EXERCISE",
          "parentId": null,
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "label": "التمرين الثالث",
          "maxPoints": 8,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "يتكون التمرين من جزأين."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_part1",
          "nodeType": "PART",
          "parentId": "s2_e3",
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "label": "الجزء الأول",
          "maxPoints": null,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_part1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$g$ الدالة العددية المعرفة على $\\mathbb{R}$ بـ: $g(x)=x(x-2)$، و$(C_g)$ تمثيلها البياني كما هو موضح في الشكل المقابل."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_g_graph_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "graph",
              "value": "التمثيل البياني المعطى للدالة $g$.",
              "assetId": "s2_e3_g_graph"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_p1_q1",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3_part1",
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "label": "السؤال 1",
          "maxPoints": 0.75,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p1_q1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "احسب $g(0)$ و$g(1)$ و$g(2)$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p1_q1_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$g(0)=0$ و$g(1)=-1$ و$g(2)=0$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p1_q1_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "0.75 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_p1_q2",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3_part1",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "السؤال 2",
          "maxPoints": 1.25,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p1_q2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "بقراءة بيانية: أ) حدد اتجاه تغير الدالة $g$. ب) عين حسب قيم $x$ إشارة $g(x)$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p1_q2_solution_variation",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الدالة $g$ متناقصة تماما على $]-\\infty;1]$ ومتزايدة تماما على $[1;+\\infty[$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p1_q2_solution_sign",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "image",
              "value": "جدول إشارة $g$.",
              "assetId": "s2_e3_g_sign_table"
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p1_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1.25 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_part2",
          "nodeType": "PART",
          "parentId": "s2_e3",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "الجزء الثاني",
          "maxPoints": null,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_part2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$f$ الدالة العددية المعرفة على $\\mathbb{R}$ بـ: $f(x)=-\\frac13x^3+x^2$، و$(C_f)$ تمثيلها البياني في المستوى المنسوب إلى معلم متعامد ومتجانس."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_p2_q1",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3_part2",
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "label": "السؤال 1",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "احسب كلا من $\\lim_{x\\to+\\infty}f(x)$ و$\\lim_{x\\to-\\infty}f(x)$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q1_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$\\lim_{x\\to+\\infty}f(x)=-\\infty$ و$\\lim_{x\\to-\\infty}f(x)=+\\infty$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q1_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_p2_q2",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3_part2",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "السؤال 2",
          "maxPoints": 1.5,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أ) بين أنه من أجل كل عدد حقيقي $x$: $f'(x)=-g(x)$. ب) استنتج اتجاه تغير الدالة $f$ ثم شكل جدول تغيراتها."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q2_solution_derivative",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$f'(x)=-x^2+2x=-g(x)$. إذن $f$ متناقصة تماما على $]-\\infty;0]$ و$[2;+\\infty[$، ومتزايدة تماما على $[0;2]$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q2_solution_variation",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "image",
              "value": "جدول تغيرات $f$.",
              "assetId": "s2_e3_f_variation_table"
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1.5 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_p2_q3",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3_part2",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "السؤال 3",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أ) بين أن $A(1;\\frac23)$ نقطة انعطاف للمنحنى $(C_f)$. ب) اكتب معادلة للمماس $(T)$ للمنحنى $(C_f)$ في النقطة $A$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q3_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$f''(x)=-2x+2$، وتنعدم عند $1$ وتغير إشارتها، ومنه $A(1;\\frac23)$ نقطة انعطاف لـ$(C_f)$. ومعادلة المماس هي $(T):y=x-\\frac13$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q3_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_p2_q4",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3_part2",
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "label": "السؤال 4",
          "maxPoints": 0.75,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q4_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أ) تحقق أنه من أجل كل عدد حقيقي $x$: $f(x)=\\frac13x^2(3-x)$. ب) استنتج إحداثيي نقطتي تقاطع $(C_f)$ مع حامل محور الفواصل."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q4_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$f(x)=\\frac13x^2(3-x)$، ومنه $(C_f)\\cap(xx')=\\{O(0;0),B(3;0)\\}$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q4_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "0.75 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_p2_q5",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3_part2",
          "orderIndex": 5,
          "label": "السؤال 5",
          "maxPoints": 1.75,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q5_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "احسب $f(-2)$ و$f(4)$ ثم ارسم $(T)$ و$(C_f)$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_p2_q5_solution_values",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
